snippet.title: Salaar Telugu Trailer | Prabhas | Prashanth Neel | Prithviraj|Shruthi|Hombale Films|Vijay Kiragandur
snippet.description:
Please…I…Kindly…Request!🔥
Presenting the Trailer of #SalaarCeaseFire


From the Makers of  "KGF: Chapter 1 & 2," &  the visionary director Prashanth Neel, comes a film that will push the boundaries of cinematic brilliance, presenting you the official teaser of "Salaar", featuring the powerhouse talents of Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Tinu Anand, Eshwari Rao, Jagapathi Babu, Sriya Reddy, Garuda Ram.  
Brace yourself for an extraordinary tale of rebellion filled with power-packed action and impactful music by Ravi Basrur. 
Rebel Star Prabhas shines as Salaar, Directed by Prasanth Neel, and produced by Hombale Films, this teaser offers a thrilling glimpse into the intense narrative and mind-blowing visuals that await you. 
Get Ready to Rebel with us and witness the most violent man on screens this Dec 22, 2023.

SALAAR MOVIE CREDITS:
Studio : Hombale Films
Producer : Vijay Kiragandur
Story - Screenplay - Direction : Prashanth Neel 
Salaar Star Cast - Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Hassan

snippet.title: Thankamani | Teaser | Dileep | Ratheesh Reghunandan | Super Good Films | Saina Music | Iffaar Media
snippet.description:
Thankamani is an upcoming Indian Malayalam-language crime thriller film written and directed by Ratheesh Reghunandan and Produced by R B Choudhry under the banner of Super good films in association with Iffaar Media Raaffi Mathirra. The film stars Dileep and is based on a real-life incident that occurred in Thankamany in October 1986. Thankamani Music Rights has been acquired by Saina Music.

Written & Directed by Ratheesh Reghunandan
Produced by  RB Choudary , Raaffi Mathirra
D.O.P Manoj Pillai
Editor Shyam Sasidharan
Music William Francis
Executive Producer Sujit J Nair
Sound Design Ganesh Marar-Sreejesh Nair (Mixing)
Lyrics B T Anil Kumar
Art Director Manu Jagadh
Makeup Roshan
Costume Designer Arun Manohar
Stunts Rajasekhar, Supreme Sundar, Mafia Sasi, Stun Shiva
Project Designers Sajith Krishna, Ashokan AMrutha
Production Controller Mohan (Amritha)
Project Head Sumith B P
Asso. Directors Abhijith PR, Jophin Vargheese
Colorist Liju Prabhakar
VFX Eggwhite
Stills Shalu Peyad
Design Adsofads
Marketing & Distribution Dream Big Films

snippet.title: Khumar Episode 04 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - 2nd December 2023
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khumar Episode 04 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 2nd December 2023 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Cast:

Khumar Episode 03 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 1st December 2023 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Cast:
Feroze Khan as Faiz
Neelam Muneer as Hareem

snippet.title: FURIOSA : A MAD MAX SAGA | OFFICIAL TRAILER #1
snippet.description:
This is her Odyssey. #Furiosa - Only in Theaters 2024

Anya Taylor-Joy and Chris Hemsworth star in Academy Award-winning mastermind George Miller’s “Furiosa: A Mad Max Saga,” the much-anticipated return to the iconic dystopian world he created more than 30 years ago with the seminal “Mad Max” films.  Miller now turns the page again with an all-new original, standalone action adventure that will reveal the origins of the powerhouse character from the multiple Oscar-winning global smash “Mad Max: Fury Road.”  The new feature from Warner Bros. Pictures and Village Roadshow Pictures is produced by Miller and his longtime partner, Oscar-nominated producer Doug Mitchell (“Mad Max: Fury Road,” “Babe”), under their Australian-based Kennedy Miller Mitchell banner. 

As the world fell, young Furiosa is snatched from the Green Place of Many Mothers and falls into the hands of a great Biker Horde led by the Warlord Dementus.  Sweeping through the Wasteland, they come across the Citadel presided over by The Immortan Joe.  While the two Tyrants war for dominance, Furiosa must survive many trials as she puts together the means to find her way home.

Taylor-Joy stars in the title role, and along with Hemsworth, the film also stars Alyla Browne and Tom Burke. 

Miller penned the script with “Mad Max: Fury Road” co-writer Nico Lathouris.  Miller’s behind-the-scenes creative team includes first assistant director PJ Voeten and second unit director and stunt coordinator Guy Norris, director of photography Simon Duggan (“Hacksaw Ridge,” “The Great Gatsby”), composer Tom Holkenborg, sound designer Robert Mackenzie, editor Eliot Knapman, visual effects supervisor Andrew Jackson and colorist Eric Whipp. The team also includes other longtime collaborators: production designer Colin Gibson, editor Margaret Sixel, sound mixer Ben Osmo, costume designer Jenny Beavan and makeup designer Lesley Vanderwalt, each of whom won an Oscar for their work on “Mad Max: Fury Road.” 

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents, in Association with Village Roadshow Pictures, A Kennedy Miller Mitchell Production, A George Miller Film, “Furiosa.”  The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, in theaters only nationwide on May 24, 2024 and internationally beginning on May 22, 2024.

Episode 3944: Swagat Samaroh Hua Flop
--------------------------------------------------------
When Jethalal and Tapu try to open the door of the car, they fail. Jethalal tells Tapu that the car door must be stuck, so they try again, but this time someone else comes out of the car. When Jetha tries to open the door on the other side, Sundar gets down. Jetha searches inside the car and finds Daya is not there. What will Jetha's next reaction be? Stay tuned!

snippet.description:
The eleventh studio recorded single, written, sung and composed by #AnuvJain is here!

Listen to 'Husn' on all streaming platforms - https://anuvjain.lnk.to/Husn

For inquiries - anuvjain.work@gmail.com
Instagram - @anuvjain
Manager- aayushman@representmgmt.in

Music production - Angad Bahra, PUNA
Mix and Master - Angad Bahra (Uneven studios)
Dolby Mix - Mukul Jain (Ferris Wheel Studios)
Acoustic Guitars - Harsimran Singh Bhatia

Project Managers: Madhura Rumde, Tanvi Seth

Production House: EO2 EXP
Video Producers - Risheeta and Rishabh Agrawal
Director - Pankhuri Ranjan 
Executive Producer - Farzeen Khan
Associate Producer - Ramin Yazeshani
Financial Controller - Karpu Swami
DOP - Leslie D’souza
1st AD - Malhar Wakde
DA - Smera Juneja
2nd AD - Rupali Khandelwal

Lead male actor - Tejas Ravishankar
Lead female actor - Vidushi Kaul
Production Manager -Tanvi Agarwal
Costume Stylist - Ayushi & Rajvee 
Hair & Makeup Artist - Sapna
Production Designer - Anish Pandey

Choreographer - Neeraj Lohani 

Post Producer -  Priti Rai 
Associate Post Producer - Rishabh Agarwal
Editor - Nathan Dcosta
Grade Artist - Uday Oswal

HUSN lyrics

Paragraph 1

Dekho Dekho 
Kaisi baatein yahan ki 
Hain saath par 
Hain saath na bhi
Kya itni aasaan hain?

Dekho Dekho 
Jaise mere iraaday
Waise kahaan 
Tere yahan the
Haan kitni naadan main

Chorus 1

Mere husn ke ilawa
Kabhi dil bhi maang lo na
Haye pal mein 
Main pighal jaun haan 

Ab aisa na karo 
Ke dil judna paye wapis
Teri baaton
Se bikhar jaun haan 

Paragraph 2

Mana zamana hai deewana
Isilye tune na jana 
Tere liye main 
Kaafi hoon 

Dekho Dekho 
Yeh zamane se thak kar 
Atey ho kyun masoom ban kar?
Tere liye main 
Kya hi hoon?

Chorus 2

Phir aatey kyun yahan
Karne aankhon mein 
Ho baarish?
Ab aye 
Toh theher jao na

Aur poocho na zara 
Mere din ke bare mein bhi
Bas itne mein 
Sambhal jaun haan 

Pre – Bridge

Haan ek din 
Kabhi koi 
Jab bhi padhe 
Kahani teri

Lagta mujhe
Mere naam ka 
Zikr kahin 
Bhi hoga nahin

Bridge

Haan 
Main yahin 
Meri yeh aankhon mein 
Aankhon mein toh dekho 

Dekho yeh dil ka haal kya 
Hothon se hota na bayan 
Meri yeh aankhon mein 
Aankhon mein toh dekho 

Kaisa naseeb hai mera
Milke bhi na mujhe mila 
Meri yeh aankhon mein 
Aankhon mein toh dekho 

Teri adhuri si wafa 
Maangu main maangu aur na 
Meri yeh aankhon mein 
Aankhon mein toh dekho 

Paragraph 3

Dekho Dekho
Kaisi kheenchi lakeerein
Chahe bhi dil toh bhi na jeete
Main iss daud mein nahin

Dekho Dekho 
Kaisi baatein yahan ki 
Baatein yahi dekhoon jahan bhi 
Main is daur se nahin

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg sub_confirmation=1

Bhide gets new swing for his balcony. Jethalal and Daya get nostalgic about the old days. Champaklal and Jethalal talk about the good old days. But the swing situation isn't going in favour for Bhide.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 753
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #comedy2023 #jethalal 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: TOUGH COOKIES! Clash of Clans Clashmas Season Challenges
snippet.description:
This Clashmas ain't your average cookie-cutter celebration! Turn your enemies into crumbs this holiday season with the Gingerbread Hero Skins! Unlock the Gingerbread Warden with December's Gold Pass! 


Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. http://supr.cl/ThisArmy

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

snippet.title: BAMBOO CHICKEN | Chicken Cooking in Bamboo | Direct Fired Bamboo Chicken Recipe Cooking in Village
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cut 4 big-sized bamboo trees to make bamboo chicken recipe. We first marinated all the chicken with masala and then put it in bamboo to cook on a direct fire. 

The bamboo chicken recipe is one of the unique and traditional recipe. It gives the chicken an awesome smell and taste while cooked by direct fire!

snippet.title: Exit Polls Results | Favor to Congress | కాంగ్రెస్‌కు అనుకూలంగా ఎగ్జిట్ పోల్స్ ఫలితాలు
snippet.description:
రాష్ట్రంలో తొలిసారి కాంగ్రెస్... అధికారంలోకి వచ్చే అవకాశముందని మెజార్టీ ఎగ్జిట్ పోల్స్  అంచనా వేశాయి. 60 స్థానాలకుపైనే హస్తం పార్టీ సాధించే అవకాశం ఉన్నట్లు దాదాపు అన్ని సర్వే సంస్థలు తెలిపాయి. భారాస ప్రతిపక్ష పాత్రకే.. పరిమితం కావొచ్చని పేర్కొన్నాయి. మూడు, నాలుగో స్థానాల్లో భాజపా, MIM నిలొవచ్చని ఎగ్జిట్  పోల్స్  వెల్లడించాయి

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3943 | 1 Dec 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3943: Sundar Ka Intezaar
--------------------------------------------------------
Champaklal has made special sweet treats on the account of  Daya's return. Tapu Sena is excited to taste the special sweet delicacy prepared by Champaklal. Goli is challenged by Tapu Sena to take the "sukdi" out of Champaklal's hand. Tapu calls Sundar to find out where he is. Finally, a car arrives at Gokuldham and everyone thinks Daya is inside the car. Has Daya really arrived at Gokuldham?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3943, 1 Dec 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.title: CID के सामने किसने मारी छलाँग? | CID | Unusual Investigations |28 Nov 2023 l Full Episode | सी.आई.डी
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

Team CID is called in a posh society to investigate a situation. The flat in which this incident took place was locked most of the time as per a resident. Eventually, the residents decide to break the door and enter the flat. But, when they entered the flat they were left puzzled as things normal. Later, CID starts investigating the same.

Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1494
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #सीआईडी #CID2023 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #LIVCrime #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #LatestCID

About CID:
-----------------
Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch all episodes of 'Unusual Investigations':
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIXvhXkbwjwhfRbDsJkUK3ws

snippet.title: पालक पनीर ऐसे बनायेंगे तो सब तारीफ करेंगे।Bhuna Palak Paneer Recipe। Lasooni Palak Paneer
snippet.description:
#palakpaneer #paneer #winterspecial 
Moms Palak Paneer 

INGREDIENTS TO MAKE THE RECIPE:

1 tsp Sugar 
350 Gms Palak 
3 Gree chillies 
Coriander Stems (some)
1 tsp Oil (for Grinding Palak)

For Masala 
2 Laddle Mustard Oil 
1 Inch Ginger 
5 - 6 big Garlic Cloves 
2 Onion 
3 Tomatoes 
1 tsp Jeera 
2 Tej patta 
1/2 tsp Haldi Powder 
1 tsp Red Chilli Powder 
2 tsp Coriander Powder
1.5 Salt 
4 Tbsp Curd 
1 tsp Garam Masala 
1 tsp Kasuri Methi 
1 Tbsp Atta 
Coriander Leaves 
2 Tbsp Malai 
400 Gms Paneer

For Tadka 
2 tsp Desi ghee 
 4 Garlic Cloves (chopped)
2 dried Red Chillies 
1/2 tsp Kashmiri Red Chilli Powder

snippet.title: Dunki Drop 3: Nikle The Kabhi Hum Ghar Se | Shah Rukh Khan | Rajkumar Hirani | Pritam,Sonu N,Javed A
snippet.description:
The terrible sense of longing to return to one’s homeland never goes away. Witness Hardy, Manu, Buggu, and Balli’s dream to see their home and loved ones come true in the song #NikleTheKabhiHumGharSe

#Dunki, starring Shah Rukh Khan, Taapsee Pannu, Boman Irani and Vicky Kaushal, is a saga of friendships, borders, nostalgia for home and love.

Directed by Rajkumar Hirani, and presented by Jio Studios, Red Chillies Entertainment and Rajkumar Hirani Films.  

Releasing worldwide in cinemas on 21st December, 2023.

snippet.title: Humko Tumse (Official Video Song) | Jubin Nautiyal | Rocky Khanna | Shreya Chaudhry | Jyoti | RadF
snippet.description:
'I will look for you in every lifetime until we finally stay ‘. "Humko Tumse" is here to Celebrate the passion and intensity of Love.

Humko Tumse Song Lyrics:
'Humko Tumse Pyar Hai Kitna 
Kaise Hum Samjhayenge
Humko Tumse Pyar Hai Kitna 
Kaise Hum Samjhayenge

Simte Huwe Se Yeh Mere Iraade
Tumko Sada Hi Chahenge
Kya Rakha Hai Aur Iss Dil Mein
Kaise Batlayenge
Dil Ko Cheer Ke Apna Dikha Dein
Tum Jo Kaho Mar Jaayenge
Humko Tumse Pyar Hai Kitna 
Kaise Hum Samjhayenge

Humko Tumse Pyar Hai Kitna 
Kaise Hum Samjhayenge

Tu Jo Kahe Toh Duniya Bhula Dein
Yeh Bhi Tu Aazma Le
Shiddat Itni Meri Wafaa Mein
Tera Bhi Dil Pighla Dein
Kya Maqsad Hai
Aur Iss Dil Ko Kitna Sataoge
Tum Na Mile To Karte Hain Wada
Phir Na Kisiko Chahenge

Humko Tumse Pyar Hai Kitna 
Kaise Hum Samjhayenge

Tu Jo Na Ho Toh
Tujhse Aakhir Kaise Hum Keh Paayein
Itni Bechaini Hai Aakhir
Kaise Dil Behlaaein
Aag Lagi Hai Jo Iss Dil Mein
Kaise Hum Bujhayenge
Roshan Jo Ho Teri Duniya
Tere Liye Jal Jaayenge
Humko Tumse Pyaar Hai Kitna 
Kaise Hum Samjhayenge

Itni Zaalim Hai Teri Yaadein 
Haste Haste Rulaa Dein
Tujhse Kate Din
Tujhse Hi Raatein
Kaise Hum Ye Bhula Dein
Qatra Qatra Aur Iss Dil Ko Kitna Rulaoge
Tod Diya Ye Dil Jo Tumne 
Phir Bhi Tumko Chahenge

Humko tumse pyaar hai itna 
Kaise hum samjhayenge'

#HumkoTumse #JubinNautiyal #NewSong

snippet.title: DAD vs SON - a college cultural | Hari Baskar
snippet.description:
Join us in this entertaining tale of a college student, eager to break free from the routine, as he plans to bunk college for the much-anticipated cultural festival. Watch the drama unfold as his carefree day takes an unexpected turn when his dad decides to accompany him, throwing a wrench into his plans. Will he manage to sneak away and meet his friends for a day of fun and partying, or will his dad's surprise inspection ruin the escapade? Find out in this rollercoaster of a day filled with laughter, unexpected twists, and the age-old battle between freedom and responsibility. Subscribe now for a story you won't want to miss! 🎉📚 #CollegeLife #haribaskar #dadvsson

snippet.title: Double Dhamaal Movie Scenes | How did Kabir become so Paisewala? | Riteish Deshmukh | Arshad Warsi
snippet.description:
How did Kabir become so Paisewala? Double Dhamaal, also known as 420s or Super Kameenas,  is a 2011 Indian Hindi-language comedy film and is directed and produced by Indra Kumar. After losing a huge sum to a police officer, four slackers find themselves unemployed and broke. They then come up on the police officer, who now apparently lives a wealthy lifestyle with his wife. They intrude in his life and blackmail him.

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3942: Sundar Ka Vaada
--------------------------------------------------------
The news that Daya will finally return on Diwali has everyone at Gokuldham excited. Taarak confides in Anjali that he has a feeling that something strange will occur and that things won't go as planned. He informs Anjali that Daya Bhabhi's plan is still a mystery and that he does not believe anything Sundar says. Anjali asks him to keep quiet so as not to spoil Jetha's delight, but Tarak has already asked Jetha what's on his mind. Stay tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3942,30 Nov 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Double Dhamaal Movie Scenes | Anda-murga chod, tera toh poppat ho gaya Tony | Riteish Deshmukh
snippet.description:
Anda-murga chod, tera toh poppat ho gaya Tony. Double Dhamaal, also known as 420s or Super Kameenas,  is a 2011 Indian Hindi-language comedy film and is directed and produced by Indra Kumar. After losing a huge sum to a police officer, four slackers find themselves unemployed and broke. They then come up on the police officer, who now apparently lives a wealthy lifestyle with his wife. They intrude in his life and blackmail him.

snippet.title: Sandeep Reddy Vanga & Bhushan Kumar Interview on Animal, Ranbir Kapoor, SRK, Prabhas, & Allu Arjun
snippet.description:
In a candid chat with Pinkvilla, Sandeep Reddy Vanga and Bhushan Kumar open up on their December 1 release, Animal starring Ranbir Kapoor, Anil Kapoor, Bobby Deol and Rashmika Mandanna. The duo inform why Ranbir deserves the term superstar and label him the most versatile actor in today’s time. Sandeep confesses that it’s his dream to direct Shah Rukh Khan in a feature film, and promises a new Prabhas in Spirit. Bhushan Kumar believes that Allu Arjun’s persona will soon get a Sandeep Reddy Vanga touch, and goes back in time to inform how Ranveer Singh missed out on Kabir Singh. Sandeep terms Bhushan the best producer, whereas the latter is excited to do back-to-back films with his director. Watch this full video here!

#ranbirkapoor #animalmoviereview #pinkvilla

snippet.title: PM Modi ने Uttarkashi Tunnel से बाहर निकाले जाने के बाद की मजदूरों से फोन पर बात
snippet.description:
Uttarkashi Tunnel Rescue | पीएम मोदी ने उत्तरकाशी के टनल से 41 मजदूरों को बाहर निकाले जाने के बाद उनसे फोन से बातचीत की. मोदी ने कहा कि हमारे श्रमिक भाइयों के रेस्क्यू ऑपरेशन की सफलता हर किसी को भावुक कर देने वाली है. टनल में जो साथी फंसे हुए थे, उनसे मैं कहना चाहता हूं कि आपका साहस और धैर्य हर किसी को प्रेरित कर रहा है. इसके साथ ही कहा कि मैं आप सभी की कुशलता और उत्तम स्वास्थ्य की कामना करता हूं.


PM Modi spoke to 41 laborers over phone after they were taken out from the tunnel of Uttarkashi. Modi said that the success of the rescue operation of our labor brothers is going to make everyone emotional. I want to say to the friends who were trapped in the tunnel that your courage and patience is inspiring everyone. Along with this, I wish all of you well and good health.
